Package: AnaCoDa
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Codon Data under Stationarity using a Bayesian
        Framework
Version: 0.1.3.0
Date: 2019-05-11
Authors@R: c(person("Cedric", "Landerer", role = c("aut", "cre"), email
